# Installation

Install pipx:
```shell
apt install pipx
pipx ensurepath
```

Install docker-inspector via pipx:
```shell
pipx install docker-inspector
dinspect
```

# Development

Run locally:

 - `textual console -x EVENT -x DEBUG`
 - `textual run --dev docker_inspector.app:run`

Publish:

`poetry publish --build`

